### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### 1. Get all doctors (should be empty initially)
GET {{baseUrl}}/doctors

### 2. Create first doctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. Sarah Smith",
  "speciality": "Cardiology",
  "email": "sarah.smith@medibook.com",
  "phone": "+1-555-0101",
  "license_number": "DOC-12345",
  "bio": "Board-certified cardiologist with 15 years of experience",
  "photo_url": "https://via.placeholder.com/150"
}

### 3. Create second doctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. Michael Johnson",
  "specialty": "Neurology",
  "email": "michael.johnson@medibook.com",
  "phone": "+1-555-0102",
  "license_number": "DOC-67890",
  "bio": "Specialist in neurological disorders and brain surgery"
}

### 4. Get all doctors again (should show 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/doctors

### 5. Get specific doctor (ID 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/doctors/1

### 6. Update doctor
PUT {{baseUrl}}/doctors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "Board-certified cardiologist with over 20 years of experience specializing in interventional cardiology"
}

### 7. Delete doctor
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/doctors/2